<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Olympus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Olympus,</orth> the mountain which was the residence of the ancient gods: <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 11</bibl>. Proverbially high: <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 3.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. III, 1, 74</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.277" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 277</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>